To properly execute files:

./bufr_upa2ob.x gdas.adpupa.tHHz.YYYYMMHH.bufr YYYYMMDDHH
./bufr_craft2ob.x gdas.aircft.tHHz.YYYYMMHH.bufr YYYYMMDDHH
./bufr_aircar2ob.x gdas.aircar.tHHz.YYYYMMHH.bufr YYYYMMDDHH
./bufr_sat2ob.x gdas.satwnd.tHHz.YYYYMMHH.bufr YYYYMMDDHH

./runob2lit_imd_obs.x files.txt YYYYMMDDHH

To convert muliple files, place input BUFR data in bufrdecodelr/bufrobs,
and edit and run the convert.csh script accordingly. Output data will 
be placed in bufrdecodelr/lrobs.
